    Scope and Contents
Physical Sciences Program records (1970-81) consist of description and proposal establishment of Physical Sciences Program, meeting minutes, agenda, memos, brochures and program sponsored events.  The Physical Sciences Program sought to provide students with a solid foundation in the physical sciences, a perception of the major problems facing society and sufficient background to facilitate solutions.  The program was terminated in 1981.  
  
